<template><AdminPage title="TMDB 数据导入" kicker="External Source" hint="从 TMDB 批量同步热门影片、类型、演职员与海报资料。"><div class="surface-card admin-import-panel"><div><h3>热门影片批量导入</h3><p>导入会按 TMDB ID 去重；已有影片会更新资料，不会产生重复记录。</p></div><el-slider v-model="limit" :min="1" :max="50" show-input/><button class="pill-button is-active" :disabled="loading" @click="run">{{loading?'正在同步…':`导入 ${limit} 部影片`}}</button><div v-if="result" class="admin-import-result"><div><b>{{result.imported}}</b><span>成功导入</span></div><div><b>{{result.skipped}}</b><span>跳过</span></div><div><b>{{result.requested}}</b><span>请求数量</span></div></div></div></AdminPage></template>
<script setup>import{ref}from'vue';import{ElMessage}from'element-plus';import{importPopularMovies}from'@/api/adminManagement';import AdminPage from'@/components/admin/AdminPage.vue';const limit=ref(20),loading=ref(false),result=ref(null);async function run(){loading.value=true;try{result.value=(await importPopularMovies(limit.value)).data;ElMessage.success('TMDB 数据同步完成')}finally{loading.value=false}}</script>
